title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft & Avionics Update 2 - final build available?
description:
In this video we will go through the changes in what is likely going to be the final beta build of Aircraft & Avionics Update (AAU) 2. This makes this update very likely the release candidate version which eventually will be offered to everyone. The list of fixes is pretty limited compared to all previous builds so it is more polishing the update.
